---
// ProblemStatement.astro — Section 2: Abstract
---
<section id="problem-statement" class="content-section">
  <div class="section-container">
    <h2 class="section-heading reveal">System-Level Bottlenecks in Perception-Faithful Replay</h2>

    <div class="prose reveal">
      <p>
        Mobile robots operate in dynamic, uncertain environments where rare failures and near-misses are inevitable. Yet, reconstructing what truly happened remains a fundamental challenge.
      </p>

      <div class="problem-highlights">
        <p>
          Existing approaches are limited in three key ways:
        </p>
        
        <div class="highlight-box">
          <div class="highlight-item">
            <span class="highlight-number">1</span>
            <div class="highlight-content">
              <h4>Incomplete Evidence</h4>
              <p>External sensors miss internal autonomy states and decisions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="highlight-item">
            <span class="highlight-number">2</span>
            <div class="highlight-content">
              <h4>Infeasible Recording</h4>
              <p>Full-resolution logging exceeds onboard compute and storage budgets.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="highlight-item">
            <span class="highlight-number">3</span>
            <div class="highlight-content">
              <h4>Distorted Replay</h4>
              <p>Motion-induced artifacts corrupt sensor data, causing replay to diverge from real behavior.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="conclusion">
        These limitations make failure analysis unreliable and hinder continuous system improvement.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
    word-break: break-word;
  }

  .section-heading::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 48px;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .prose {
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  .prose p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    word-break: break-word;
  }

  .prose p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Problem Highlights Section */
  .problem-highlights {
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .problem-highlights > p {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .highlight-box {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .highlight-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(192, 94, 60, 0.05) 0%, rgba(27, 42, 74, 0.03) 100%);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .highlight-item:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(192, 94, 60, 0.08) 0%, rgba(27, 42, 74, 0.05) 100%);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(27, 42, 74, 0.08);
  }

  .highlight-number {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .highlight-content h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .highlight-content p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .conclusion {
    margin-top: 1.75rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: rgba(27, 42, 74, 0.04);
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  /* Tablet (768px and below) */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-heading {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .section-heading::after {
      width: 40px;
    }

    .prose p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .problem-highlights {
      margin: 1.5rem 0;
    }

    .highlight-box {
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .highlight-item {
      padding: 1rem;
      border-left-width: 3px;
    }

    .highlight-number {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .highlight-content h4 {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .highlight-content p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .conclusion {
      padding: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
  }

  /* Mobile (480px and below) */
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .section-heading {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .section-heading::after {
      width: 35px;
    }

    .prose p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
      margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
    }

    .problem-highlights {
      margin: 1.25rem 0;
    }

    .problem-highlights > p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .highlight-box {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 0.85rem;
    }

    .highlight-item {
      padding: 0.9rem;
      gap: 0.8rem;
      border-left-width: 3px;
    }

    .highlight-number {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .highlight-content h4 {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    .highlight-content p {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .conclusion {
      padding: 0.9rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      border-left-width: 3px;
    }
  }

  /* Extra Small (320px and below) */
  @media (max-width: 320px) {
    .section-heading {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .prose p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .highlight-item {
      padding: 0.8rem;
      gap: 0.6rem;
    }

    .highlight-number {
      width: 30px;
      height: 30px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }

    .highlight-content h4 {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .highlight-content p {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    .conclusion {
      padding: 0.8rem;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
  }
</style>
